<p>Dear&nbsp;{{{Recipient.Name}}},</p>

<p>Hope you’re doing well! We noticed you’ve started exploring Serpent, and we just wanted to check in.</p>

<p>If you haven’t had the chance to dive into all the features yet, no worries. We’re here to help you get the most value from the platform. Whether you need tips, a walkthrough, or help with a specific use case, our team is happy to assist.</p>

<p>Want a personalised onboarding session? You can book a time that suits you <a href="https://outlook.office365.com/book/serpentmeetings@tekunda.com/">using this link</a></p>

<p>Your feedback is incredibly important to us, so if you have any questions, thoughts, or suggestions, just hit reply, we’d love to hear from you.</p>

<p>Looking forward to supporting your journey with Serpent!</p>

<p>Best Regards,<br />
Serpent Team<strong>&nbsp;|</strong>&nbsp;Tekunda<br />
